            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei aeterni. <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/21"
                            >Berengarius</persName> divina favente clementia <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >imperator</rs> augustus. Noverit omnium fidelium sanctae Dei Ecclesiae
                        nostrorumque presentium scilicet ac futurorum industria, <persName
                            key="#Count #fidelisOf" ref="#people/188">Grimaldum</persName> gloriosum
                            <rs key="#Emperor/king">comitem</rs> nec non et <persName
                            key="#Marquis/duke #fidelisOf" ref="#people/1502">Odelricum</persName>
                        inclitum <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchionem</rs> dilectissimos <rs
                            key="#fidelisOf">fideles nostros</rs> humiliter nostram exorasse
                        clementiam, quatenus quandam <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> iuris regi nostri
                        quae <geogName
                            key="#Houses #Rivers #Mountains #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Iudiciaria #Decima #Districtio #Churches #Royal_slave"
                            ref="#estates/1404">Girpa</geogName> nominatur simul cum <rs
                            key="#Churches">capella</rs> in honore <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1404">domini Salvatoris</orgName> consecrata
                        pertinentem videlicet de <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/124">Veronensi</geogName> cum
                        omnibus adiacentiis et pertinentiis suis ex integro, sicut dudum de eodem
                        comitatu pertinuit, <persName key="#Count #fidelisOf" ref="#people/165"
                            >Ingelfredo</persName> glorioso comiti dilectoque fideli nostro iure
                        proprietario concedere dignaremur. Quorum precibus acclinati, prenominatam
                        curtem Girpam simul cum capella in honore domini Salvatoris constructa,
                        sicut huc usque de comitatu Veronensi pertinuit, cum omnibus adiacentiis et
                        appendiciis suis suoque domo cultili, <rs key="#Houses">casis</rs>
                        videlicet, <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder"
                            >pratis</rs>, pascuis, <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, salectis,
                        sacionibus, <rs key="#Rivers">aquis aquarumque decursibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Mills">molendinis</rs>, <rs key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Royal_slave">servis et ancillis</rs>, venationibus, <rs
                            key="#Districtio">districtionibus</rs>, <rs key="#Iudiciaria"
                            >iudiciariis</rs>, <rs key="#Decima">decimis</rs> cunctisque ad se
                        pertinentibus iuste et legaliter tam in <rs key="#Mountains">montibus</rs>,
                        vallibus quamque in planiciebus Ingelfredo glorioso comiti <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >iure proprietario</rs> concedimus et largimur, ac de nostro iure et
                        dominio in eius ius et dominium omnino transfundimus atque donamus ad
                        habensum, tenendum, vendendum, commutandum, alienandum, pro anima iudicandum
                        et quicquid voluerit faciendum absque totius potestatis contradicitone, si
                        quis igitur hoc nostrae auctoritatis et concessionis preceptum infringere
                        vel violare temptaverit, sciat se <rs key="#Penalty">compositurum auri
                            optimi libras centum</rs>, <rs key="#Camera_regis">medietatem camerae
                            nostrae</rs> et <rs key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem
                            predicto Ingelfredo</rs> glorioso comit[i s]uisque heredibus vel cui
                        ipse dederit aut habere concesserit. Quod ut verius credatur et diligentius
                        observetur, manu propria roborantes de anulo nostro subter insigniri
                        iussimus. Signum domni (MF) Berengarii serenissimi imperatoris. <persName
                            key="#Chancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/1501">Iohannes</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> et <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs>
                        ad vicem <persName key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/216"
                            >Ardingi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi. (SR) (SI n° III
                        framm.)</ab>
